column2: SELECT TOP # input.OBJID AS akari_ID, input.RA AS akari_ra, input.DEC AS akari_dec, sp.z AS redshift, out.distance into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.akari_subset AS input CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (input.RA, input.DEC, #) AS out INNER JOIN DR1#.SpecPhoto AS sp ON out.objid = sp.specObjID
